channel.title: Te Mana Kuratahi 2025
channel.desc: LIVE: Te Mana Kuratahi Kapa Haka 2025 will bring together the top primary school kapa haka from across Aotearoa. These kapa haka have earned their place at National level through regional competition and will gather at Bay Park Arena, Tauranga from Monday 3 November to Friday 7 November 2025.
